flowchart TB
    subgraph Input[Input]
      A[Input Parameters\n- Keyword / Topic ID\n- Date Range\n- Region Filter\n- Run Mode]
    end

    A --> B[Stage 1: Paper Fetch\n(stage1_discover.py)\nQuery OpenAlex (topic or search), paginate, save JSONL]
    B --> C[Stage 2: Author Extraction\n(stage2_extract.py)\nExtract authorships, dedupe, build author_map]

    C --> D[Parallel Batch Processing]

    subgraph Parallel[Parallel Enrichment]
      direction LR
      D1[Stage 3a: Author Enrichment\n(stage3_enrich.py)\nprofiles & metrics]
      D2[Stage 3b: Co-author Analysis\n(graph & relationships)]
      D3[Stage 3c: Institution Enrichment\n(institution metadata)]
    end

    D --> Parallel
    Parallel --> E[Stage 4: Assemble & Upsert\n(stage4_assemble.py + db.py)\nbatch upserts to MySQL, create embeddings, upsert to Pinecone]

    E --> Stores[Data Stores\n- MySQL (researcher_db)\n- Pinecone (embeddings)\n- JSON / Excel summaries]

    subgraph Ranking[Ranking Service (Phase 2)]
      direction TB
      Rapi[Rank API\n(rank_service.py / api.py)]
      Remb[Compute Embedding\n(embeddings.py)]
      Rpine[Pinecone Query\n(candidate paper matches)]
      Rq[Compute Q (query relevance)\n(ranking.py: compute_q_weighted)]
      Rh[Compute H (impact)\n(ranking.py: compute_h)]
      Rcomb[Combine H & Q -> final_score\n(final_score())]
      Rapi --> Remb --> Rpine --> Rq --> Rcomb
      Stores --> Rh --> Rcomb
      Rcomb --> Response[API Response\n(results + components + reason + contribution)]
    end

    UserQuery((User Query + Filters)) --> Rapi
    Response --> Feedback{Backfill / Recovery Needed?}
    Feedback -->|Yes| Inject[Inject specific works or add topic to `CONCEPTS`]
    Inject --> B
    Feedback -->|No| Done((Done))

    %% Configuration and tuning
    Config[Config & Weights\n`config.py`\nH_WEIGHT, Q_WEIGHT, H_COMPONENT_WEIGHTS, Q params]
    Config --> A
    Config --> Ranking

    classDef box stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,fill:#fff
    class A,B,C,D,Parallel,E,Stores,Rapi,Remb,Rpine,Rq,Rh,Rcomb,Response,Feedback,Inject,Config box
